This project implemented "game of life" game.

Ruby version : 1.9.3
Install libraries by running "bundle install"

Users :

Start Game by running "rake play"
Run all tests by running "rake test"

Developers :

This project is currenlty implemented for two dimensional mat. This project is scalable 
in design to extend this to multiple dimensions in future.

Game rules are defaulted to default rule. This project is scalable to include multiple rules.

